ZH: 我许诺会帮你完成这个任务。
EN: I promise to help you complete this task.

ZH: 我们需要得到许可才能进入那个建筑。
EN: We need permission to enter that building.

ZH: 他在参观展览时许下了一个愿望。
EN: He made a wish when visiting the exhibition.

ZH: 这个讲座让我许多新的知识。
EN: This lecture provided me with a lot of new knowledge.

ZH: 请不要许下不能兑现的承诺。
EN: Please do not make promises that you cannot keep.

ZH: 我们需要以书面形式许可你的项目。
EN: We need to grant permission for your project in writing.

ZH: 这个公司的政策不许员工私自升职。
EN: The company's policy does not allow employees to be promoted without authorization.

ZH: 她用手臂许下一个心愿，闭上眼睛默默祈祷。
EN: She crossed her arms and silently prayed, making a wish.

ZH: 请以书面形式提出许愿申请。
EN: Please submit your wish application in writing.

ZH: 我们不能许可任何违反规定的行为。
EN: We cannot allow any behavior that violates the regulations.

ZH: 许多人认为他是一位伟大的领导者。
EN: Many people consider him a great leader.

ZH: 他许久未曾回家。
EN: He hasn't been home for a long time.

ZH: 这是一个无法被许可的行为。
EN: This is an act that cannot be permitted.

ZH: 他许多年都在这个城市工作。
EN: He has been working in this city for many years.

ZH: 她许一个人生的承诺。
EN: She made a lifelong commitment to someone.

ZH: 这个建筑许多年来一直是城市的地标。
EN: This building has been a landmark of the city for many years.

ZH: 他的许愿得到了实现。
EN: His wish has been fulfilled.

ZH: 许多人前来参加他的婚礼。
EN: Many people came to attend his wedding.

ZH: 我许多次询问过那个问题，但没有得到答案。
EN: I have asked that question many times, but have not received an answer.

ZH: 他许诺要帮助我学习汉语。
EN: He promised to help me learn Chinese.
